          {
            "id": "c0245ab9-ee35-4f6c-8116-963e1744a1e2",
            "text": "The item wasn’t the issue because when we received it, it was the wrong set. Then we were not able to exchange for the correct set which were the exact same price, no difference and then the set of EarPods we needed clearly stated in stock at this specific location which is why we ordered them here and after not being able to find an associate to help us, the girl in customer service told us they were in the back and didn’t even get anyone to help us with them if she couldn’t help us herself.",
